            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27838968">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27838968/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p27838968-2.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">最近看张爱玲的小说和赵珩的《老饕漫笔》也都提到了藤萝饼，这么风雅的美食市面上怎么就没了，残念
