 </span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27838968/">(<span class="">3回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-07-29 20:01</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                最近看张爱玲的小说和赵珩的《老饕漫笔》也都提到了藤萝饼，这么风雅的美食市面上怎么就没了，残念
<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.douban.com/subject/10784961/">http://www.douban.com/subject/10784961/</a>
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p27838968-2.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







